</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【unwire TV】【專訪】 中大「毒魔」般的史萊姆機械人，最新變形、再生、外太空使用、醫療應用曝光</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/04/26/unwire-tv-cuhk-venom/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=unwire-tv-cuhk-venom</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[nickman]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 26 Apr 2022 13:00:10 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[unwire TV]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1097442</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>專訪中大「毒魔」Venom 般的史萊姆機械人 ! 最新變形、再生、外太空使用、醫療應用曝光！ &#160;</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>專訪中大「毒魔」Venom 般的史萊姆機械人 ! 最新變形、再生、外太空使用、醫療應用曝光！<br />&nbsp;<br /><iframe loading="lazy" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=314&#038;href=https%3A%2F%2Fbusiness.facebook.com%2Funwirehk%2Fvideos%2F395230422238880%2F&#038;show_text=false&#038;width=560&#038;t=0" width="560" height="314" style="border:none;overflow:hidden" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="true" allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowFullScreen="true"></iframe></p></p><div class="feedflare">
